      "title": "A series of explosions and fires in southern Thailand",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Reuters reported that a series of explosions and fires have occurred in at least 17 places in southern Thailand. The Thai security forces said that the chain of events was well planned and carried out.",
        "These fires and explosions have taken place in the early hours of today (17) targeting fuel stations and shops in 3 provinces in southern Thailand. Seven people have been slightly injured as a result of these incidents, the Thai security forces said. The news service reported."
      ],
